<p>How quickly we forgot the crisis in 2020.  New York City, an early epicenter, was  “<a href="https://www.npr.org/sections/health-shots/2020/05/28/863710050/reckoning-with-the-dead-journalist-goes-inside-an-nyc-covid-19-disaster-morgue" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">so inundated with corpses that they were just incapable of holding them all”</a> with bodies stored in refrigerated trucks. Hospitals and health systems were overwhelmed, with sick patients lying on gurneys in the hallway or in their cars in the parking lots. I could go on here, but you certainly remember the picture. </p><p>There were projections going back to April 2020 that <a href="https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/31/us/coronavirus-vaccine-timetable-concerns-experts-invs/index.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">we could have a vaccine to protect us from the virus within 18 months.</a> Most of us didn’t believe that was remotely possible, knowing the average time it took for a successful vaccine directed against <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/04/30/opinion/coronavirus-covid-vaccine.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">a new pathogen was over 8 years</a>. And that’s not including the many that have failed, despite attempts over several decades, like HIV, tuberculosis, CMV, and plenty of others. T<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2020/04/30/opinion/coronavirus-covid-vaccine.html" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">he realistic projection was pegged to November 2033</a>. That date is not a typo!</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F92f3aa1d-0f39-4335-9431-12c4aaae91fa_1584x1146.png" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/cW0YPPS-q4qPx3a10Qmbm3WcmHjZyQWUcirJl4da-14=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkY5MmYzYWExZC0wZjM5LTQzMzUtOTQzMS0xMmM0YWFhZTkxZmFfMTU4NHgxMTQ2LnBuZw== 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Baptsc9w66nuQL6m9ruqvczSKDdiq9uK-VpNT9gqixQ=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGOTJmM2FhMWQtMGYzOS00MzM1LTk0MzEtMTJjNGFhYWU5MWZhXzE1ODR4MTE0Ni5wbmc= 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/1WNS1gr3- 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/K6PcrH1DyW5jFQTrD-M2YRIn9Hb9_" alt="" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/hwnwFE7CSY6JpcCX1Qn0bT2fBUfmwix2iPUpnq3W_gk=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkY5MmYzYWExZC0wZjM5LTQzMzUtOTQzMS0xMmM0YWFhZTkxZmFfMTU4NHgxMTQ2LnBuZw== 424w, https://reader.miniflux. 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/lqw5Du3xe3fqlpnILmrXILP4JX- 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/K6PcrH1DyW5jFQTrD-M2YRIn9Hb9_ 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"/></picture></a></figure><p></p><p><a href="https://erictopol.substack.com/subscribe?" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Subscribe now</a></p><p>As you well know, in the United States and other countries, mRNA Covid vaccines began distribution in December 2020, an unprecedented accelerated timeline in the same calendar year that SARS-CoV-2 was sequenced. Two large Phase 3 randomized trials, with over 74,000 participants (at their completion, not from any early interim analysis), demonstrated 95% reduction of symptomatic Covid. Here’s the <a href="https://twitter.com/EricTopol/status/1332771238771630080" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">Table I made back</a> then summarizing how rapidly this took place.</p><figure><a href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fbe58b74c-781a-47b0-bbb1-977001b44323_4096x3031.jpeg" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/_9cU8Ud-nwh6zYYZccOGM1FZtLaAyJuO1Tv_jDKq1zA=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX3dlYnAscV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZiZTU4Yjc0Yy03ODFhLTQ3YjAtYmJiMS05NzcwMDFiNDQzMjNfNDA5NngzMDMxLmpwZWc= 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/zMCfz8dsNus0jYEVj_-_ 848w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/m8KFg5g2IAA7nE0w3Edca7xlMqPVN8ILA_XfBuPSpiM=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd18xMjcyLGNfbGltaXQsZl93ZWJwLHFfYXV0bzpnb29kLGZsX3Byb2dyZXNzaXZlOnN0ZWVwL2h0dHBzJTNBJTJGJTJGc3Vic3RhY2stcG9zdC1tZWRpYS5zMy5hbWF6b25hd3MuY29tJTJGcHVibGljJTJGaW1hZ2VzJTJGYmU1OGI3NGMtNzgxYS00N2IwLWJiYjEtOTc3MDAxYjQ0MzIzXzQwOTZ4MzAzMS5qcGVn 1272w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/kseTYNMmg_ 1456w" sizes="100vw"/><img src="https://reader.miniflux." alt="Image" title="Image" srcset="https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/xN7JTYhga9cXsXHZR2k7HhZ_3jWd14_ZUW8iqXl9dPI=/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdWJzdGFja2Nkbi5jb20vaW1hZ2UvZmV0Y2gvd180MjQsY19saW1pdCxmX2F1dG8scV9hdXRvOmdvb2QsZmxfcHJvZ3Jlc3NpdmU6c3RlZXAvaHR0cHMlM0ElMkYlMkZzdWJzdGFjay1wb3N0LW1lZGlhLnMzLmFtYXpvbmF3cy5jb20lMkZwdWJsaWMlMkZpbWFnZXMlMkZiZTU4Yjc0Yy03ODFhLTQ3YjAtYmJiMS05NzcwMDFiNDQzMjNfNDA5NngzMDMxLmpwZWc= 424w, https://reader.miniflux.app/proxy/Cq_0l7A0AISFdUl_GsuE6WVm8IWoJ-kB1NeHLx